perl-spiffy: perl-spiffy (Framework for doing object oriented programming in Perl)
perl-spiffy:
perl-spiffy: "Spiffy" is a framework and methodology for doing object oriented (OO)
perl-spiffy: programming in Perl. Spiffy combines the best parts of Exporter.pm,
perl-spiffy: base.pm, mixin.pm and SUPER.pm into one magic foundation class. It
perl-spiffy: attempts to fix all the nits and warts of traditional Perl OO, in a
perl-spiffy: clean, straightforward and (perhaps someday) standard way.
perl-spiffy:
perl-spiffy: http://search.cpan.org/dist/Spiffy/
perl-spiffy:
perl-spiffy: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
